en_598539_0	16 Vijayabahu Infantry Regiment of the Security Force Headquarters - Jaffna (SFHQ-J) taking an initiative organized a Yoga training session for the troops serving in areas under the SFHQ-J during June 8-9.
en_598539_1	The programme was conducted on the instructions of Major General Darshana Hettiarachchi, Commander, Security Forces - Jaffna in order to strike a balance between the body and the mind.
en_598539_2	A large gathering of Officers and Other Ranks attended the training session.
